---
description: CareSutra UI brand rules
alwaysApply: true
---

CareSutra UI must follow the approved web brand system.

Palette:
- Trust Blue: #1F4E79
- Support Blue: #2E6AA6
- Heritage Gold: #C8A24D
- Soft Gold: #E3C77A
- Ivory: #F7F4ED
- Charcoal: #2E2E2E

Typography:
- Montserrat for body, navigation, buttons, forms, labels, admin UI
- Cormorant Garamond for hero and premium section headings

Design principles:
- Minimal, premium, trustworthy, supportive
- Prefer ivory/white backgrounds
- Use blue and gold accents sparingly
- Avoid harsh black borders
- Avoid clutter
- Avoid generic SaaS UI
- Use soft shadows, rounded-2xl cards, readable spacing
- Keep mobile-first responsiveness

Logo:
- Use /caresutra-hr-logo.svg unless a newer simplified SVG is added
- Do not stretch, skew, recolor, or redesign the logo
- Keep clear spacing around the logo
